# Ripgrep-only whitelist (git does not read this file).
# opencode's grep/glob tools run ripgrep with default ignore rules, so the
# gitignored test-playground/ would be invisible to agent searches. .ignore
# outranks .gitignore for ripgrep, so this line re-includes the fixture for
# search while git continues to ignore it. node_modules/ stays excluded via
# the root .gitignore.
!test-playground/
